Imagine you wake up one morning and all humans have disappeared, what do you do?
If you could speak to any person living or dead, who would it be, and why, what would you ask them ?
Imagine you're on a sinking ship, and enough lifeboats for half the passengers, how do you decide who gets a spot on the lifeboat?
If you could master any skill or knowledge without any effort, what would you choose and why, how would you use it?
Suppose you have the chance to create a new holiday that everyone in the world would celebrate, what would it commemorate and how would people celebrate it?
Imagine you could implement a global law that everyone must follow, what law would you create and what impact would it have?